OL,3,C'Irreversible' damage caused as group
OL,4,C'remove artefacts' from 'haunted'
OL,5,Ccastle
OL,7,FA group of people have caused
OL,8,F"irreversible" damage to a protected
OL,9,Fsite at a Devon castle while removing
OL,10,Farchaeological artefacts, English
OL,11,FHeritage has said.
OL,13,FIt was reported around six people went
OL,14,Fto Berry Pomeroy Castle on Sunday 28
OL,15,FJanuary with a metal detector 'under
OL,16,Fthe cover of darkness'.
