OL,7,FThe site near Totnes was built in the
OL,8,Flate 15th century and became home to
OL,9,Fthe Seymore family - to whom Jane
OL,10,FSeymore, third wife of Henry VIII,
OL,11,Fbelonged - in 1547.
OL,13,FIt has long been thought to be haunted
OL,14,Fand boasts a rich history.
OL,16,FWin Scutt, senior properties curator
OL,17,Fat English Heritage, said staff who
OL,18,Farrived on Sunday morning found
OL,19,Fnumerous holes in the ground, as well
OL,20,Fas rubbish strewn across the site.
