OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police have
OL,8,Freleased the following pictures and
OL,9,Fare appealing for information.
OL,11,FWin Scutt said: "Damage caused to the
OL,12,Farchaeology of scheduled monuments by
OL,13,Funauthorised use of metal detectors is
OL,14,Ftaken seriously by the law and by the
OL,15,Fpolice, who are appealing for
OL,16,Finformation.J"The damage caused by
OL,17,Funskilled digging of holes on a
OL,18,Fnationally important site like this is
OL,19,Firreversible.
