OL,7,F"We shall never know how much
OL,8,Fknowledge has been lost about the
OL,9,Fhistory of Berry Pomeroy Castle due to
OL,10,Fthis disturbance of the buried
OL,11,Farchaeology.J"Berry Pomeroy Castle was
OL,12,Fbuilt as a defended residence of the
OL,13,FPomeroy family in the 15th century and
OL,14,Flater had a large Elizabethan house
OL,15,Fconstructed within its walls.
OL,17,F"It is one of the largest and most
OL,18,Fimpressive castles in southwest
OL,19,FEngland.
