OL,7,F"Because of this importance, it is
OL,8,Fprotected as a Scheduled Monument and
OL,9,Fis also in the Guardianship of the
OL,10,FSecretary of State and in the care of
OL,11,FEnglish Heritage."
OL,13,FPC Julian Fry said: This incident took
OL,14,Fplace in the early hours of Sunday
OL,15,Fmorning under the cover of darkness.
